 class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.37</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (s.v.l.); [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἀλέξανδρος] ἐπλάζετο ἄγων [Ἑλένην]</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:117\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.117</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:116\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">116</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀκταῖσιν ὁρμεῖ, δαρὸν ἐκ Τροίας χρόνον ἄλαισι πλαγχθείς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg016.perseus-grc1:56\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">56</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of an exile, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ἄργεϊ νάσθη πλαγχθείς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:120\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.120</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γένεσις καὶ ὄλεθρος τῆλε μάλ᾽ ἐπλάχθησαν</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have been banished</tr_> afar, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1562.tlg001:8:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Parm.\">Parm.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.28</biblScope> </bibl> : metaph., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ νέος . . ὑπὸ τῆς τύχης . . πλάζεται, ὁ δὲ γέρων καθάπερ ἐν λιμένι τῷ γήρᾳ καθώρμικεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:gr